PrecisAmendments to the GALLANTRY AWARDS ORDER which increase the annuity payable to holders of the Victoria Cross or the George Cross, from $300 to $3,000, and transfer responsibility for paying benefits from the Canadian Pension Commission to the Minister of Veterans Affairs.

precis:
Amendments to the GALLANTRY AWARDS ORDER which increase the annuity payable
to holders of the Victoria Cross or the George Cross, from $300 to $3,000,
and transfer responsibility for paying benefits from the Canadian Pension
Commission to the Minister of Veterans Affairs.
